{
  "texts": [
    "The model is described in its own node.",
    "A Model is in a relation with its Deployment.",
    "The relation (edge) is named, though the named edge is not depicted here.",
    "A model can be deployed repeatedly, as is captured by the 1:m n-ary relationship between a model and an intstance of its deployment.",
    "A deployed model serves the role of the Inference Execution Instance of Figure 1 in that it captures information about the behavior of inference server in use.Persistent storage is through a graph database (Neo4j)."
  ]
}